Package: icdsnomedr
Type: Package
Title: ICD to SNOMED CT Concept Mapper for OMOP CDM
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("4ramvarma", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Maps ICD-9 and ICD-10 codes to SNOMED CT concepts using the 
    Observational Medical Outcomes Partnership (OMOP) Common Data Model (CDM).
    Provides direct mappings and hierarchical fallback mechanisms with 
    confidence scoring and manual review flagging.
